1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,375
Before compression, there is only abundance — more than the world can hold.

2
00:00:03,375 --> 00:00:06,750
Find the peak. Everything else is measured against it.

3
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:10,125
To be quantized is not to be lost — it is to be known by your essential value.

4
00:00:10,125 --> 00:00:13,500
Two become one. Even and odd, packed together — memory, halved.

5
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,875
Smaller. Faster. Still true. The approximation that preserves the soul.
